{"tid":383471,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［浸大］想做嘉倩bb同學","createTime":"2017-09-01T13:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T14:09:59.000Z","uid":56377,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83128a9c9c25fce30bfd661a2b6514ad1d4ce714","tid":383471,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:33:29.000Z","msg":"TVB美女主播陳嘉倩由於樣貌甜美，被網民叫佢「嘉倩BB」，平時喺公仔箱見佢報道新聞，估唔到有機會同佢做同學!<br />\n<br />\n嘉倩BB今日喺Ig貼出浸大學生證，留言：「各位同學仔加油！今日我都要開學。」打hashtag「學生時代我又返嚟啦」、「還未懂世故的那一年」，嘉倩BB於2012年中大英文系畢業，2013年入nowTV新聞部做主播，2014年過檔TVB新聞及資訊部做無綫新聞主播，一直宅男愛戴。<br />\n<br />\n唔少網民估佢係讀master，再睇佢張學生證要讀兩年先畢業，而且後面有啲關於傳理學院嘅資料，有網民讚佢可愛、又有網民叫佢加油，另有網民口花花留言「我係妳啲同學，就一定無心機上堂」、「張學生相咁瘦嘅」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/01/212051_461b8971dfa75a0a8e6be89e887f21d3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F01%2F212051_461b8971dfa75a0a8e6be89e887f21d3.jpg&h=441ef84f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/01/212051_1c01262d936dec5b7d969615d054adfe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F01%2F212051_1c01262d936dec5b7d969615d054adfe.jpg&h=655347c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機會黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fb8303bea7a4cd3c32cdcb27c47c2171cc7dca","tid":383471,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"我中學師姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f95a912561acacc93e746eda32cd65aaf3010a","tid":383471,"uid":59961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"真係咁靚咩😓"}]}